Steps to login in G5K
----------------------------------------------------
1. ssh account@access.grid5000.fr
2. Connect to a selected site, such as luxmbourg
3. Reserve a node : oarsub -I -l nodes=1,walltime=1:45 -t deploy
4. Deploy the OS : kadeploy3 -f $OAR_NODE_FILE -e jessie-x64-base -k
5. Connent to the node root@NODENAME
6. Start the blockchain installation

We need to use the Ruby-Cute to autimate all nodes reservation and deplyment 


